FUENTE.+  ~6A~#122
;000536E4{$/DON GWANO IS DESPERATE. HE'S=/READYING THESE PERFUME=/FACTORIES FOR LAUNCHING=/CHEMICAL WARFARE. BLAST THEM=/OR WE'LL BE SURROUNDED BY=/STINK CLOUDS.~6A~}#155#152
