;000538D2{$/WELL, THIS IS IT - OPERATION=/BIG CHEESE. WE'VE LOCATED=/DON GWANO'S SECRET BASE.=/IT'S DEEP IN THE JUNGLE AND=/IS SURROUNDED BY HIS=/EXPERIMENTAL DEFENSES.%/IT'S A RISKY MISSION, BUT=/YOU'VE BEATEN THE ODDS SO=/FAR...PULL THIS MISSION OFF=/AND YOU'LL GO HOME A HERO.~6A~}#273#270
$/
