;00054B02{$/THE BRUTAL DICTATOR, GENERAL=/DON GWANO, HAS ATTACKED HIS=/NEIGHBORS, USING HIS OIL=/MONEY TO FUND HIS ARMY AND=/NAVY.%/WE'VE GOT TO STOP HIM, BUT=/WE DON'T WANT TO LAUNCH A=/FULL OFFENSIVE.%/I PROPOSE THAT WE BEGIN A=/TOP SECRET MISSION USING OUR=/BEST PILOT WITH OUR NEWEST=/WEAPONRY. IN A SERIES OF=/LIGHTNING STRIKES WE CAN=/REMOVE THE THREAT OF GENERAL=/DON GWANO.~6A~}#375#372
$/
